# CodeDoc

AI Agent for Codebase Documentation — reads your code and generates a living, structured Markdown reference.

## Installation

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://github.com/yourname/codedoc.git
cd codedoc

# Install (creates the `codedoc` command globally)
pip install -e .
